reviewText: Join Steve and his digital camera as he takes you on tour of the Mirage, Las Vegas Hotel & Casino, the Las Vegas residential development and landscape around Queensridge and Badlands Golf Course, and the resort area, residential and outdoor attractions of Laughlin, Nevada.  Take a vacation without leaving the home and witness the beautiful architecture, design, art, landscape and sites in the Las Vegas, Nevada area.  Sit back and enjoy the ride.
